    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ミュージックビデオ撮影当日",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ撮影が始まるぞ。準備はいいか？",
      "startTime": 2.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　いつでもいけます！",
      "startTime": 6.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2366.6667381,
          "startTime": 8.6333334048
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても凄い歓声ですね。急に決まった\nライブなのにこんなに人が集まるなんて……",
      "startTime": 13.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "サニピを応援してる人がそれだけいるってことだ\nこの歓声はさくら達が頑張ってきた結果だよ",
      "startTime": 21.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\n今回の撮影では無理を言ってすみませんでした",
      "startTime": 26.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYと同じ会場でライブをするなんて\n準備は大変でしたよね？",
      "startTime": 34.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なんとか会場の使用許可が下りて良かったよ\nそれにしてもあの時のさくらには驚いたな――",
      "startTime": 40.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん\n私、MVのアイデアを思いついちゃいました",
      "startTime": 47.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "この会場にファンのみんなを集めて\nライブをするんです！",
      "startTime": 54.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYで私達が歌った時\n私達とファンのみんなの心は確かに繋がっていました",
      "startTime": 58.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "あの時の一体感をMVでも表現出来れば、サニピを\n見たことがない人達とも、想いを繋げられるはずです！",
      "startTime": 67.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、ライブを撮影してMVにするのか……",
      "startTime": 71.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "新曲で『この指とまれ、隣の笑顔、寂しい顔も\n繋がればほら幸せ』って歌詞があるじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 82.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "人が集まって、心が一つになって、想いが繋がって\nみんなが幸せになる……",
      "startTime": 91.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "そんな曲に込めた想いを表現するには\n私達のライブを見てもらうのが一番いいと思うんです",
      "startTime": 97.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "あ……でも、やっぱり難しいかな……\nMVのために会場を押さえてライブするなんて……",
      "startTime": 106.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、やっぱりいいです！\nただの思いつきなので今のは忘れて下さい！",
      "startTime": 113.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "さくらはそうするのが一番いいと思ったんだろ？\nだったら取り消す必要はない",
      "startTime": 121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "出来ないなんて決めつけないで胸を張って提案してくれ\nその想いを実現させるのが俺達スタッフの仕事だ",
      "startTime": 127.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\n私はこの場所でMVを撮りたいです",
      "startTime": 135.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYは今の私達に出来る\n最高のステージだったから……",
      "startTime": 141.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "あの時のパフォーマンスを出来る限り再現して\n会場に来られなかった人達にも届けたいんです",
      "startTime": 147.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "この歌で私達と、会場にいるファンの人達と\nMVを見てくれるみんなの心を繋げてみせます！",
      "startTime": 155.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "必ず最高のMVにしてみせます！\nだからお願いします、ここでライブをやらせて下さい！",
      "startTime": 162.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "勢いであんなこと言っちゃったけど\nあの後すぐにいろんなところに働きかけてくれて……",
      "startTime": 172.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "本当にライブを実現させちゃうなんて\n{user}さんはやっぱり凄いです",
      "startTime": 179.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないよ。でも、俺に出来るのはここまでだ\nここから先、いい映像になるかどうかはさくら次第だ",
      "startTime": 187.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
